description:
Suspected Infected 😷 Woman Suddenly Dies💀After Being Ripped From Car 🚗 
Thoughts?

Woman fights police to her death to prevent being taken to detainment camp as the outbreak and unrest worsens throughout #China.

#Chinese police were captured on video dragging a woman from her automobile who was thought to have been infected with the #Coronavirus before the woman stopped responding altogether.

The woman can be seen on video resisting detainment as police forcefully remove her from the vehicle.

Seconds later the woman appears to be dead. However, the woman’s status is unknown.
